node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jeff DeChesare on August 18, 2021 tagging @tonyhawk. May be an image of 2 people and footwear.

node.text: I recently had the opportunity to film a skit with @tonyhawk for @spencerbarton new TV show “The Sesh” produced by @cartoon03_ . Not sure when or where its airing but I just wanted to thank Spencer and Barry for inviting me to be on the first episode and of course Tony for coming out to do this! Definitely an experience that I will never forget! #skate #skateboarding #thesesh
